                           Lowest healthcare coverage

                Business question
Which regions have the lowest healthcare coverage? 

             Query
SELECT
country_name,
MIN(coverage)lowest_coverage
FROM cancer_data
GROUP BY country_name
ORDER BY lowest_coverage;

             Insight 
This shows that regions with low coverage are likely missing out on early diagnosis and timely treatment, which increases preventable deaths.

              Recommendation
There is a need to target these regions to inccrease mobile clinics, subsidized care, and awareness campaigns.

